	<br>
	<div style="text-align:right;">
		UYETAQUI, Nicolle Sayuri França<sup>1</sup>; FREITAS, Vladimir Passos de<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
